title: New test
subtitle: A new year
on-arrival: {!
// see post_event.scene.dry for changes.
Q.resources += 2;

!}
tags: event
view-if: test_variable = 1 and test_variable_timer = 0
priority: 2
max-visits: 1

A new year begins. The economy appears to be slackening; unemployment is increasing throughout the republic, although for the most part, people are still doing well.

- @nothing_to_test: There is nothing we can do.

@nothing_to_test
on-arrival: welfare -= 1; workers_spd -= 3; unemployed_spd -= 3; pro_republic -= 3

There is, essentially, nothing we can do.
